title: Stunning One Bedroom at Grand & Syndicate
posting_body: ['Property Address', '35 Syndicate St S - 407 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Stunning One Bedroom at Grand & Syndicate', 'Contemporary elegance meets old-world charm in the plush G floor design.', 'This stunning top-floor apartment features a private east-facing deck, updated lvp flooring throughout, and a two entry-way closet.', 'An in-home washer and dryer, dishwasher, and center island are just part of what makes this outstanding home so special.', 'Enjoy the perks of a rooftop lounge and patio at Grand and Syndicate.', 'The Grand Life at your doorstep.', 'Coffee shops, pubs, dining, universities, and so much more await you on trendy Grand Avenue in Historic Saint Paul.', 'Live one block from beautiful Summit Avenue with biking lanes, N.I.C.E. ride bikes, and metro transit near your doorstep.', 'It’s all right here.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Keyless Entry', 'Washer/Dryer in Apt', 'Granite Countertop', "9' Ceilings", 'Rooftop Lounge & Patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Elevator', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Vinyl Tile Plank Flooring', 'Fitness at the Grand Clubhouse', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', '24-hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Smoke-Free Living', 'Management Office on-site', 'Year Built: 2018', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 780', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,925.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
